{
  "stem": "16106.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I grabbed the gun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I grabbed my old guard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I had the-- we were hopping, hopping, hopping back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the mean guy was standing by the window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I waived my passport from [? far. ?] He was-- And do you know what?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I had my own room from then on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And soldiers were sleeping in front of the door so the bad guy shouldn't puzzle me anymore till they got deported.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now we all Germans had to be deported to [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hela, ?] Peninsula [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hela. ?] That was the last-- the last place was still under Nazi, as far as I know, Peninsula [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hela. ?] So they were there, lying there along the [INAUDIBLE], along that river.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the first SS came and went on that boat, whatever that is, then the officers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the soldiers came, and they couldn't take anything with them to have more space, and the women.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, here, this is my chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, why don't you go ahead?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will wait for the next boat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why don't you-- and next was the next ferry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And did I get compliments.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only a German woman can be so brave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Only a German woman is so selfless.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Only a German woman can be anything I am.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I am absolutely the [INAUDIBLE] and the [INAUDIBLE] all turned into one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They couldn't get [? where-- ?] they couldn't be grateful enough for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were lying [? there ?] as the Russians were bombing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it was over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't have any more boats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went back to the-- and there were no Germans, no boats.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Rolf, ?] from the office came over and said to me, Veronica, he said, learn something in life.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
